::Battera::

She looked at the him.  This part snake and scorpion bot looking up 
at her.  "Look, if I'm bothering you. I'll leave.  I'm just out 
flying high and having fun." She smiled hoping that would convince 
him.  She wasn't trying anything or wanting a fight.  She was in 
happy mood and didn't want it to change right then.
